{"tid":1717861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【保密身份方法大整合】大家一齊靜靜地贏","createTime":"2019-11-13T16:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T18:01:21.000Z","uid":202895,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74d67204808deff5c3dd244956e111b9b1ad01ff","tid":1717861,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">古語有云：「沉默是金」</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n1. 鏡頭前戴返個口罩（<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>尤其是食野飲水個陣，一係開遮擋住食啦，一係一睇到就上返口罩</strong></span>）<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔好係CCTV下同他人眼光下換裝（<strong><ins>哨兵眼前</ins></strong>都係）<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔好係<strong><ins>任何地方同任何人</ins></strong>透露發夢細節，包括上<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>家長車</strong></span>個陣都係<br />\n<br />\n4. 唔好打卡，唔好Post手足動靜（包括新發明）<br />\n<br />\n5. 唔好對記者咁友好，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保持警惕</strong></span></strong>（慎防紅媒）【知唔知道最親近人類嘅流浪貓狗係最危險，同理】<br />\n<br />\n6. 留意有冇人跟蹤，參考多個反跟蹤方法，例如行快後突然急停等等&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n7. 唔好係被D奇怪嘅人R你傾計個陣，同佢講<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任何野</span></strong>，請無視佢，仲有提下隔離手足<br />\n<br />\n8. 大戰時不透露大隊行蹤比記者，不被鏡頭聽到討論結果<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n個人最希望大家留意係第5點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝大家靜靜地贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6214a66968b687a70aad3a75fe616efc90b2557","tid":1717861,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"搵人幫手推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望多D人睇到"},{"pid":"ede6d6d484b5641a4010b440121880dbd7aca2ef","tid":1717861,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"同時歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9251963b7529eb910521fc251721bda51a8810d1","tid":1717861,"uid":180716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17cfd2ef8c5c5474ab4443d39d451c8903e0e5a6","tid":1717861,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6563f2b6f9d7ee72d91c3273952bec5954613fce","tid":1717861,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:04:16.000Z","msg":"仲有就係唔好過份blackbloc<br />\n哨兵就唔好黑衫啦，街坊裝就得<br />\n<br />\n9. 我愛風褸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb569fbd730b0584f465283dada74a313f0107a","tid":1717861,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790b94d6999d500141945e722e0ef9c3ab4e0834","tid":1717861,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87390e7ee5d02bd84c6abd43298b81b91dea8f31","tid":1717861,"uid":64159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74d67204808deff5c3dd244956e111b9b1ad01ff","tid":1717861,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">古語有云：「沉默是金」</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac